description: Try our easy to follow Beef Stroganoff With Beans recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Stroganoff,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Green beans,Low sugar,Sesame free,Beef,Mushroom,High protein,Soy free,Peanut free
name: Beef Stroganoff With Beans Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 750g beef rump steak, cut into 2cm strips

recipeInstructions.text: Place flour in a snaplock bag. Add beef strips. Seal bag and shake to coat. Remove beef. Place in a bowl.
Heat 2 tbs oil in a large, heavy based saucepan over medium high heat. Cook beef in batches, set aside and keep warm.

Add remaining oil to pan add onion and mushrooms, cook over medium heat for 5 minutes and return beef to pan. Add paprika, garlic and tomato paste cook for a further 1 minute. Add Campbells Real Stock Beef, stir to combine and bring to the boil, reduce heat to low and simmer covered for 15 minutes. Remove lid stir and cook for a further 15 minutes, uncovered.
Stir through sour cream just before serving.
Serve with green beans and either rice, mashed potato or pasta.
